headline: Corpay and Computer Guidance Corporation Release New Case Study Highlighting Integrated AP Automation
summary: Corpay, a global leader in business payments, and Computer Guidance Corporation, a leading provider of construction enterprise resource planning (ERP) software, today announced the release of a new joint case study showcasing the impact of their integrated accounts payable (AP) automation solution for mutual customer, S.T. Wooten.
